quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  48,10,"Those who swore fealty to you, (O Prophet), in fact swore fealty to Allah. The Hand of Allah is above their hands. So whoever breaks his covenant breaks it to his own hurt; and whoever fulfils the covenant that he made with Allah, He will bestow on him a great reward."{1}{2}{3},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2,footnotes:3:3